data.description: A great investment opportunity in the up-and-coming Lents neighborhood. Zoned commercial/mixed use, this 2 bed, 1 bath fixer is waiting for your creative touch to transform it into your dream home or multi-unit investment property. With some essential updates already in place including an updated electrical panel, newer gas water heater, and some pex plumbing this property offers immense potential and is conveniently situated for an easy commute to all your favorite Portland destinations. Walkable to plenty of bars, cafes and restaurants; whether you're heading downtown, to the airport, nearby parks, or exploring the eclectic neighborhoods that make Portland unique, you're just moments away from all the action. An investor's dream offering the perfect canvas for renovation and customization, don't miss out on unlocking the potential of this hidden gem. [Home Energy Score = 6. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10222335]
